Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:38.84,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}脚步就愈发紧凑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:41.84,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}跨越时光
